        "cases": [
            {
                "input": {
                    "parameter_name_1": "value_1",
                    "parameter_name_2": "value_2"
                },
                "expected": "expected exception or behavior",
                "description": "clear scenario description and test intent"
            }
        ]
    }
]
```

